messages.content:
You are an expert web designer. Your task is to assign appropriate component categories to each section of the website based on the provided plan.



Instructions:
1. Analyze the website plan
2. For each section in each page, select the most appropriate component category from the available categories
3. Output a JSON structure with pages and their sections mapped to component categories

Format:
{
    "page_name": {
        "section_name": "component_category",
        ...
    },
    ...
}

message.content:
```json
{
    "Homepage": {
        "Hero Section": "hero",
        "Key Achievements & Stats": "stats",
        "Client Logos Showcase": "logos",
        "Testimonials": "testimonials",
        "Core Services with Pricing Plans": "services",
        "Footer": "footer"
    },
    "About/Contact Page": {
        "Team Introduction": "team",
        "Agency Growth Timeline": "timeline",
        "FAQ Section": "faq",
        "Contact Section": "contact",
        "Footer": "footer"
    }
}
```

